lead_paragraph: Chelsea's renaissance under Antonio Conte comes under renewed scrutiny when the Premier League leaders visit Manchester City this weekend on the back of a seven-match winning streak.

headline.print_headline: Conte's High-Flying Chelsea Face Tough Test at Man City
